Create a dynamic project
Copy following jars from struts 2 lib folder to our project's WEB-INF\lib folder
	commons-fileupload-1.3.1.jar
	commons-io-2.2.jar
	commons-lang-2.4.jar
	commons-lang3-3.2.jar
	commons-logging-1.1.3.jar
	commons-logging-api-1.1.jar
	freemarker-2.3.19.jar
	javassist-3.11.0.GA.jar
	ognl-3.0.6.1.jar
	struts2-core-2.3.20.3.jar
	xwork-core-2.3.20.3.jar
Create Action Class with setter and getter
Create views

Create WebContent/WEB-INF/classes/struts.xml
Add StrutsPrepareAndExecuteFilter in web.xml

Enable Detailed Log:
	WebContent/WEB-INF/classes/logging.properties
Execute the Application